# --- harness data (results + gold are reproducible / large; not source) ---
# results/* = JSONL ledgers + results/transcripts/*.json · data/ = copied/symlinked gold · .worktrees/ = scratch worktrees per (infra_repo, ref)
# results/showcase.jsonl is the ONE published exception: the sanitized public showcase
# ledger (scripts/make_showcase.py strips previews/paths/session ids before it exists).
results/*
!results/showcase.jsonl
data/
.worktrees/
